title: Test your social autism
author: VD
content_html: Take the test. As before, I’m interested in knowing your religious self-identification: theist, agnostic or atheist. My AQ is 9, by the way. I think I scored an 11 the last time I took the test, so obviously the Nintendo Wii has made me more social.
